<UCPnum.AuthorBioInCatalog><DATA><b>David Attwell</b> is Senior Lecturer at the University of Natal in Pietermaritzburg, South Africa. Attwell is also the editor of <i>J.M. Coetzee, Doubling the Point: Essays and Interviews</i> (1992).</DATA></UCPnum.AuthorBioInCatalog>
